short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Outback Equipment Searcher: Administration and Management Tool.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SKU Link Inserter is a productivity tool designed for e-commerce professionals who frequently need to access product details and stock levels in the cPanel. This extension automatically adds clickable links to the product pages, enabling quick access to product information and stock levels directly from the SKU displayed on product pages.
